OL,3,CNew flagship store set to delight
OL,4,CHarry Potter fans
OL,6,FA Harry Potter flagship store is to
OL,7,Fopen in London's Oxford Street in the
OL,8,Fautumn, Warner Bros has announced.
OL,10,FThe planned 21,000 sq ft shop over two
OL,11,Ffloors within The Ribbon development
OL,12,Fat 134-140 Oxford Street will become
OL,13,Fthe second official Harry Potter
OL,14,Fretail destination in the UK after a
OL,15,Fsite at King's Cross Station.
OL,17,FWarner Bros said designers planned to
OL,18,Ftransform the interior of the building
OL,19,Finto a "wizarding emporium celebrating
OL,20,Fthe beloved locations featured in the
OL,21,Fbooks and films".
