OL,3,CNew flagship store set to delight
OL,4,CHarry Potter fans
OL,6,FKarl Durrant, Warner Bros senior vice
OL,7,Fpresident of worldwide retail, said:
OL,8,F"Harry Potter isdeeply rooted in
OL,9,FBritish storytelling, and this will
OL,10,Fgive fans an exciting new way to
OL,11,Fexperience this magical world in the
OL,12,Fcity that features so prominently in
OL,13,Fthe stories.
OL,15,F"Offering a completely new retail
OL,16,Fexperience for Harry Potter fans which
OL,17,Fwill delight and entertain, it's going
OL,18,Fto be very special."
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@AOUzD@TO]
