OL,3,CNew flagship store set to delight
OL,4,CHarry Potter fans
OL,6,FThe new shop will join the collection
OL,7,Fof Harry Potter experiences owned and
OL,8,Foperated by Warner Bros in London
OL,9,Fincluding Warner Bros Studio Tour
OL,10,FLondon ` The Making of Harry Potter
OL,11,Fand the Harry Potter shop at King's
OL,12,FCross.
OL,14,FLondon Mayor Sir Sadiq Khan announced
OL,15,Fin February that plans to ban traffic
OL,16,Ffrom part of Oxford Street have been
OL,17,Fapproved.
OL,19,FVehicles will be prohibited from
OL,20,Faccessing a 0.7-mile stretch between
OL,21,FOxford Circus and Marble Arch.
