OL,3,CNew flagship store set to delight
OL,4,CHarry Potter fans
OL,6,FOxford Street is one of the world's
OL,7,Fbusiest shopping areas, with around
OL,8,Fhalf a million visitors each day.
OL,10,FWorks to pedestrianise the road are
OL,11,Fexpected to start in the summer, with
OL,12,Fthe first traffic-free section
OL,13,Fintroduced by the end of the year.
